import { Box, TextField, MenuItem, FormControl } from "@mui/material";

const Register = () => {
  return (
    <Box
      sx={{
        display: "flex",
        flexWrap: "wrap",
        width: 500,
        border: "1px solid black",
      }}
    >
      Register
      <Box component="form" noValidate autoComplete="off">
        <FormControl>
          <TextField type="text" label="Nume" variant="outlined" />
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl>
          <TextField type="email" label="Email" variant="outlined" />
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl>
          <TextField type="password" label="Parolă" variant="outlined" />
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl>
          <TextField
            type="password"
            label="Confirmare parolă"
            variant="outlined"
          />
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl>
          <TextField
            label="Sex"
            variant="outlined"
            select
            sx={{ width: 75 }}
            value=""
          >
            <MenuItem value=""></MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="m">M</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="f">F</MenuItem>
          </TextField>
        </FormControl>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Register;
